      "gloss": "The specialized alchemical furnace designed to maintain a gentle, perfectly constant heat for months or even years without interruption, incubating the transformative vessel.",
      "facet": "It is an exterior architectural tool that directly mirrors the interior heat of the alchemist's soul; the fire in the furnace and the fire in the mind must burn in absolute unison.",
      "provenance": "Detailed explicitly in the works of Geber ('Summa Perfectionis') and established in later European operational laboratory manuals."
