      "facet": "It signifies the permanent fixation of the volatile spirit. The alchemist does not merely return to Edenic innocence, but forges an entirely new, indestructible divine consciousness.",
      "provenance": "The standard final phase in foundational four-stage and three-stage alchemical models, central to Nicolas Flamel's legendary narratives."
