      "gloss": "The Allfather, god of poetry, frenzy, runes, and esoteric wisdom. Modern Heathenry emphasizes his role as a relentless wanderer who sacrifices himself to himself on the World Tree to grasp the secrets of existence.",
      "facet": "He is venerated less as an omnipotent, benevolent patriarch and more as a model of relentless self-overcoming and dangerous spiritual initiation. His wisdom is deeply tied to ecstasy and boundary-breaking.",
