      "gloss": "The red-bearded god of thunder, agriculture, and the protection of humanity. He is the warder of Midgard, actively wielding his hammer Mjölnir against chaotic forces that threaten the cosmic or social order.",
      "facet": "He is the democratic, accessible counterweight to Odin's aristocratic elitism. Modern practitioners invoke him for everyday physical strength, defense of the marginalized, and the blessing of marriages and homes.",
