      "gloss": "The esoteric and exoteric leadership of the Muslim community, vested exclusively in the purified lineage of the Prophet through Fatima and Ali. The Imams are the infallible guides and living interpreters of the Qur'an's inner meaning.",
      "facet": "While legislative revelation ended with Muhammad, divine guidance could not. The Imam serves as the cosmic pole (Qutb) without which the earth would shatter, ensuring a continuous, physical human bloodline carries the indispensable light of esoteric truth.",
