      "gloss": "The Supreme Personality of Godhead in A.C. Bhaktivedanta Swami Prabhupada's ISKCON. He is not an avatar of Vishnu, but the absolute, original source of all avatars, universes, and spiritual energies, reigning in the highest spiritual planet, Goloka Vrindavana.",
