      "gloss": "Advanced souls originating from other star systems—such as the Pleiades or Arcturus—who voluntarily incarnate on Earth. They suffer planetary amnesia but carry dormant light-codes to trigger global ascension.",
      "facet": "Metaphysically reframes modern alienation. Experiencing severe societal detachment is no longer a psychological malady, but definitive proof of an elite extraterrestrial origin and a messianic cosmic mission.",
