      "gloss": "An enigmatic infantile deity with a downturned, snarling mouth, toothless gums, and a deeply cleft head, often depicted weeping. Rendered in exquisite jade or held in the arms of rulers, it is recognized as a primeval spirit of rain, thunder, and earth.",
      "facet": "It captures the terrifying vulnerability of a divine infant—a crying baby whose tears are the rain itself, intimately linking human reproduction, infantile need, and the fierce predatory power of the jaguar.",
