      "gloss": "Massive, individuated basalt portraits of Olmec rulers, weighing up to fifty tons and transported from distant volcanic mountains. Wearing distinct helmets likely used in the ritual ballgame or for warfare, they gaze outward with powerful, heavy-lidded expressions.",
