      "gloss": "The great mother of the waters, overseeing oceans, fertility, and profound healing. She is the nurturing, 'cool' counterpart to the 'hot' male deities of iron and thunder.",
      "facet": "While originating as the Yoruba Yemoja, in Trinidad she frequently blends with St. Anne or the Virgin Mary, and sometimes overlaps with the Hindu goddess Ganga Mai, reflecting the island's unique Afro-Asian demographic crucible.",
