      "gloss": "Yéil the Raven, who found the world in darkness and stole the sun, moon and stars from the box where the rich chief Nass-shakee-yéil hoarded the light — then loosed them into the sky for all. He brings water and fire to people, gluttonous and cunning in the same breath.",
