      "gloss": "The solitary, tireless worker and fierce warrior who rules over iron, technology, forests, and war. He lives in the wilderness, perpetually clearing the path for human civilization with his machete.",
      "facet": "He is the relentless engine of labor and blood. Animal sacrifice physically requires his presence; no blood can be shed without the iron knife, making him complicit in every ritual taking of life.",
