      "gloss": "The incredibly complex system of divination governed by Orula, using sixteen cowrie shells or the ekuele chain to access the 256 Odu (signs). It reveals the blueprint of a person's destiny and the required ebbó (sacrifices).",
      "facet": "It operates almost like a massive binary computer code, mapping every possible human situation, illness, and myth onto a strict mathematical matrix that holds the memory of the entire universe.",
