      "facet": "It explicitly frames human beings as herd animals tied to the post of existence, humbling the intellect by declaring that only the grace of the herdsman can break the ropes of ego.",
      "provenance": "Pashupata Sutras (Lakulisha); Svetasvatara Upanishad; Indus Valley Pashupati seal (contested proto-Shiva)."
