      "kind": "concept",
      "name": "Haumai (Ego)",
      "archetypes": [
        "cosmic-adversary"
      ],
      "gloss": "The false sense of self or ego-centeredness. It is the core spiritual disease that separates the human soul from the divine, manifesting as lust, wrath, greed, attachment, and pride (the 'Five Thieves').",
      "facet": "Haumai is not a demonic entity or external devil; it is an internal psychological veil. It is both the primary cause of human suffering and the friction necessary for spiritual evolution.",
