      "gloss": "The active, rational principle that structures and animates the cosmos. It is not an abstract concept but an immanent, generative force—the 'seminal reason' (logos spermatikos) that unfolds the universe as a living, perfectly ordered organism according to an exact design.",
      "facet": "Unlike the transcendent Platonic forms, the Stoic Logos is strictly physical—a subtle, fiery breath intertwined with passive matter. It does not dictate order from above; it is the intelligent blueprint woven directly into the physical fabric of reality.",
