      "gloss": "A dynamic, tension-holding blend of fire and air that permeates the entire cosmos, giving it cohesion, shape, and consciousness. It is the material vehicle of the Logos, tightening and slackening to create all grades of existence.",
      "facet": "It defines a continuum of being through physical 'tension' (tonos). A stone, a tree, and a human soul are made of the exact same substance, differing only in its degree of rarefaction and active tension.",
