      "facet": "The god of the SWORN WORD: where the solar eye is moralised into the unsleeping witness of every contract, the one a liar cannot escape.",
      "provenance": "Mihr Yasht. Avestan Mithra is the tier-1 cognate of Vedic Mitra; later the namesake of Roman Mithras."
