      "facet": "The first-ancestor as ARK-BUILDER: not the man humanity descends from by death, but the king who preserves life through catastrophe, then forfeits his glory by lying.",
      "provenance": "Vendidad fargard 2; Shahnameh. Avestan Yima is the tier-1 cognate of Vedic Yama."
